                  Coady, D. (2003). Conspiracy theories and official stories. International Journal of Applied Philosophy, 17(2), 197–209.
                  {DiFonzo}, N., \&amp; Bordia, P. (2007). Rumor, gossip and urban legends. Diogenes, 54(1), 19-35.\&nbsp;
                  Fine, G. A. (2007). Rumor, trust and civil society: Collective memory and cultures of judgment. Diogenes, 54(1), 5-18.\&nbsp;
                  Foster, E. K. (2004). Research on gossip: Taxonomy, methods, and future directions. Review of General Psychology, 8(2), 78-99.\&nbsp;
