                  van Prooijen, J. W., \&amp; Van Vugt, M. (2018). Conspiracy theories: Evolved functions and psychological mechanisms. Perspectives on psychological science, 13(6), 770-788.
                  Zeng, J. (2018). Contesting rumours on social media during acute events: The 2014 Sydney siege and 2015 Tianjin blasts (Doctoral dissertation, Queensland University of Technology). Available at https://eprints.qut.edu.au/115786/.},
  journaltitle = {{DOCA} - Database of Variables for Content Analysis},
  author       = {Zeng, Jing},
